/a>\n        <code>digitsInfo</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p>可选. 默认值是 <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code>string</code></p>\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/formatCurrency#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Use <code>currency</code> to format a number as currency.</p>\n<p>Where:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>value</code> is a number.</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"api/common/NgLocaleLocalization#locale\" class=\"code-anchor\">locale</a></code> is a <code>string</code> defining the locale to use.</li>\n<li><code>currency</code> is the string that represents the currency, it can be its symbol or its name.</li>\n<li><code>currencyCode</code> is the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a> currency code, such\nas <code>USD</code> for the US dollar and <code>EUR</code> for the euro.</li>\n<li><code>digitInfo</code> See <a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a> for more details.</li>\n</ul>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/NgLocaleLocalization#locale\n - api/common/formatCurrency#description\n - api/common/formatCurrency#formatcurrency\n - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L124-L158\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts#L124-L158\n-->"
